WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: h5wcTn_0A44

NOTE Language: en

00:00:05.833 --> 00:00:10.034
Then came the collective chakra, what we call as the Vishuddhi.

00:00:10.833 --> 00:00:15.900
At the Vishuddhi Chakra they wanted to occupy the whole world.

00:00:16.967 --> 00:00:26.100
They wanted to occupy the whole world as their own to become emperors,

00:00:26.334 --> 00:00:31.200
and they formed empires and misbehaved to such an extent

00:00:31.767 --> 00:00:34.767
that it's not humanly possible to behave like that.

00:00:34.900 --> 00:00:37.067
They really were rakshasas, I should say,

00:00:37.267 --> 00:00:40.134
and those rakshas qualities are still there.

00:00:40.833 --> 00:00:44.967
In their behavior, in everything you can see how they behave

00:00:45.134 --> 00:00:49.800
towards people, treating them like that,

00:00:50.267 --> 00:00:57.100
creating people who are against spirituality,

00:00:57.767 --> 00:01:00.767
and those who are aggressive.

00:01:02.034 --> 00:01:06.334
Well, these became like a two-sided world

00:01:06.467 --> 00:01:11.000
where there are people who are aggressive,

00:01:11.767 --> 00:01:13.967
and the people who are tortured.

00:01:14.234 --> 00:01:23.867
This two-sided world exists even now, but is much less.

00:01:25.167 --> 00:01:28.967
Thanks to the collective understanding

00:01:29.034 --> 00:01:33.833
there are many good institution that were established

00:01:34.167 --> 00:01:38.767
but they are not working out, they are not so successful,

00:01:39.200 --> 00:01:45.000
because the men at the head of it are controlling, but controlling what?

00:01:45.267 --> 00:01:48.267
Not themselves – controlling others,

00:01:48.767 --> 00:01:53.967
and all their behavior has spoilt all the work of this chakra.

00:01:55.767 --> 00:01:59.767
Collectively you have, if you see around now today

00:01:59.967 --> 00:02:06.900
everywhere there’s war going on, fights going on, killing going on,

00:02:06.900 --> 00:02:12.267
destruction going on. How is it?

00:02:13.000 --> 00:02:17.867
There are so many spiritual people here now on this world.

00:02:18.200 --> 00:02:22.700
So the reason is, the spiritual people have become very quiet,

00:02:23.067 --> 00:02:26.134
very much enjoying their spiritual life,

00:02:26.867 --> 00:02:32.767
have become very quiet and very peaceful people.

00:02:33.234 --> 00:02:36.134
But that doesn't bring peace.

00:02:36.967 --> 00:02:41.833
You have to be dynamic and you have to bring peace in the world,

00:02:41.967 --> 00:02:43.900
you have to do something about it.

00:02:44.234 --> 00:02:46.967
We are very much satisfied with our progress,

00:02:47.234 --> 00:02:52.234
but we are not bothered as to see what is the progress others have done,

00:02:52.934 --> 00:02:56.000
how far they have gone, where can we meet them,

00:02:56.167 --> 00:02:57.934
what can we change them.

00:02:58.034 --> 00:03:00.501
At My level I can change many things,

00:03:00.867 --> 00:03:03.967
but at your level how many people have you changed?

00:03:04.334 --> 00:03:07.733
What have you done? That has to be said.

00:03:07.833 --> 00:03:11.967
Still you live with your ego, on the Agnya,

00:03:13.234 --> 00:03:15.900
and you are very happy with your peace,

00:03:16.034 --> 00:03:18.833
with everything you have got through Sahaja Yoga.

00:03:19.134 --> 00:03:23.034
This is the biggest calamity that the world is facing today,

00:03:23.334 --> 00:03:28.267
that those who are all so spiritual, those who have achieved great heights

00:03:28.367 --> 00:03:32.100
are least bothered as to what good has to be done.

00:03:32.467 --> 00:03:36.367
What they are doing is to enjoy their own spirituality,

00:03:37.167 --> 00:03:40.767
come to the puja, have more and more of it.

00:03:40.900 --> 00:03:47.034
But they have done no collective work to change people.

00:03:47.167 --> 00:03:50.000
Some of them are working, one or two,

00:03:50.301 --> 00:03:52.867
but the rest of them are having a good time

00:03:53.100 --> 00:03:56.767
enjoying themselves in such a manner

00:03:57.234 --> 00:04:03.067
that people accept them as great souls, good people, that's all.

00:04:03.967 --> 00:04:06.434
I would like you to now introspect

00:04:06.800 --> 00:04:09.833
and find out how much collective work you have done,

00:04:10.100 --> 00:04:14.334
how many people you have got – like that.

00:04:14.767 --> 00:04:16.967
With whom are you talking?

00:04:17.234 --> 00:04:20.234
How many people have you told about Sahaja Yoga?

00:04:20.800 --> 00:04:22.767
Only so many are there.

00:04:23.000 --> 00:04:27.934
Christ had only twelve disciples; they were much more dynamic than you are.

00:04:28.434 --> 00:04:31.000
So now you should take to the right side.

00:04:31.900 --> 00:04:35.767
And when you take to the right side we'll create dynamic people,

00:04:36.267 --> 00:04:45.167
not just some useless, patient, very quiet, peaceful people.

00:04:45.800 --> 00:04:47.800
This was not the aim of Sahaja Yoga.

00:04:48.034 --> 00:04:53.167
The aim of Sahaja Yoga is to change, change so many.

00:04:54.034 --> 00:04:57.267
And those who are doing that, all My blessings are with them.

00:04:57.867 --> 00:05:02.467
But those who are just keeping to themselves, it is not a very good thing.

00:05:02.967 --> 00:05:06.434
In your country how many people have got to Sahaja Yoga?

00:05:06.767 --> 00:05:10.833
Just find out. With how many people you have worked it out?

00:05:11.034 --> 00:05:16.034
So yours is not a complete yoga, yours is a partial yoga of the left side,

00:05:16.067 --> 00:05:19.234
where you are very loving, you are very kind, very this thing.

00:05:19.501 --> 00:05:22.819
I am not saying that you should become aggressive in any way.

00:05:22.900 --> 00:05:28.401
But even I have seen people want to be leaders, they want to be something great;

00:05:28.833 --> 00:05:31.767
but how many people have they given realization?

00:05:31.934 --> 00:05:35.334
How many people have they talked about Sahaja Yoga?

00:05:35.867 --> 00:05:38.867
I have said even in the aeroplane also you go,

00:05:39.100 --> 00:05:42.833
you walk in the street, anywhere people talk about Sahaja Yoga.

00:05:43.134 --> 00:05:47.800
But here we are using Sahaja Yoga for our greatness,

00:05:48.034 --> 00:05:52.367
for our understanding of ourselves.

00:05:52.800 --> 00:05:56.067
This is not why Sahaja Yoga has been brought to you.

00:05:56.733 --> 00:06:02.867
It has been brought to you for giving realizations to many people.

00:06:03.227 --> 00:06:06.034
I request all the younger people, younger generation

00:06:06.067 --> 00:06:09.767
not to waste their Sahaj energies

00:06:09.867 --> 00:06:12.134
on nonsense as the old people have done.

00:06:12.767 --> 00:06:15.900
You’d better go ahead and talk to people about Sahaja Yog,

00:06:16.034 --> 00:06:17.900
and spread the Sahaja Yoga.

00:06:18.200 --> 00:06:23.900
They are more interested in running schools, in looking after the destitute,

00:06:23.900 --> 00:06:26.100
doing this, - doing that – that's not your job.

00:06:26.434 --> 00:06:31.367
Your job is to create more Sahaja yogis, more Sahaja yoginis.

00:06:31.501 --> 00:06:35.934
But that is not there, what I find is it's not there.

00:06:36.267 --> 00:06:40.134
The right side is missing. You should come to the right side.

00:06:40.434 --> 00:06:46.733
Go all ahead. Nothing will happen to you. Nobody can kill you,

00:06:47.000 --> 00:06:50.900
nobody can disturb you, nobody can arrest you, take it from Me.

00:06:51.167 --> 00:06:56.000
You have powers but if you don't use them, you are like this.

00:06:57.401 --> 00:07:01.301
That is why we have come to the stagnated point

00:07:01.800 --> 00:07:04.900
that we should know we have to use our right side.

00:07:05.167 --> 00:07:07.967
Right side is very important.

00:07:08.867 --> 00:07:13.134
Next time I'll tell you about right side, what right-sided things you have.

00:07:13.267 --> 00:07:16.200
Now you cannot become left-sided whatever you may try;

00:07:16.301 --> 00:07:21.100
so you use your right side in the right direction

00:07:21.401 --> 00:07:27.733
with the right understanding, not as some sort of,

00:07:27.833 --> 00:07:35.134
I should say, very arbitrary or very dominating, like Hitlers.

00:07:35.934 --> 00:07:38.934
We have had also Hitlers among Sahaja yogis.

00:07:39.167 --> 00:07:42.034
But now the time has come for you

00:07:42.434 --> 00:07:46.234
to do something more than what the saints have done before,

00:07:46.867 --> 00:07:50.134
to work it out that way; not to keep to yourself

00:07:50.301 --> 00:07:54.767
that you have a family, you have very nice children,

00:07:54.767 --> 00:07:58.034
having, enjoying, all that – that's not the Sahaja Yoga for.

00:07:59.501 --> 00:08:04.334
Sahaja Yoga is for transforming the whole world.

00:08:05.234 --> 00:08:10.200
You have to think about it: what are you doing, where are you,

00:08:10.934 --> 00:08:14.900
and what have you achieved out of Sahaja Yoga?

00:08:15.301 --> 00:08:19.000
Then we come to the Agnya.

00:08:20.234 --> 00:08:25.434
In Agnya what has happened is Sahaja yogis are become, they have,

00:08:25.800 --> 00:08:31.800
they can bear anything, they can suffer anything – that's not we want.

00:08:32.700 --> 00:08:36.200
What we want, to remove the sufferings of others,

00:08:36.934 --> 00:08:39.100
remove the aggression of others.

00:08:39.334 --> 00:08:44.067
So we don't, that kind of organization we don't have,

00:08:44.767 --> 00:08:47.167
that kind of understanding we don’t have.

00:08:47.501 --> 00:08:52.134
And if that works out, you will be different people.

00:08:52.767 --> 00:08:59.067
So we have become like saints, you see, sitting in their hermit halls,

00:08:59.067 --> 00:09:03.934
something like that, not more than that.

00:09:04.767 --> 00:09:10.334
So better try to do something positive, without aggression.

00:09:10.501 --> 00:09:16.767
I know some of you are still very aggressive, are show-offs, I know that.

00:09:18.000 --> 00:09:25.267
But if you get into the mood of working out collectively,

00:09:26.067 --> 00:09:30.267
then you will realize what mistakes you have,

00:09:31.367 --> 00:09:37.234
still what is lacking in your personality – that is very important.

00:09:37.501 --> 00:09:41.267
At Agnya Chakra many Sahaja yogis falter,

00:09:42.833 --> 00:09:45.334
I don't know what happens to them.

00:09:46.067 --> 00:09:49.267
At Agnya I have told that you must forgive.

00:09:49.867 --> 00:09:54.100
But that doesn't mean that you allow people to do wrong things.

00:09:54.934 --> 00:09:58.234
Because you want to forgive it's very easy not to fight,

00:09:58.267 --> 00:10:02.200
not to say anything, just keep out, just forgive – no.

00:10:03.034 --> 00:10:10.334
You go and talk to that person and tell him it is wrong.

00:10:12.900 --> 00:10:14.800
You have to face it.

00:10:15.800 --> 00:10:20.967
If you cannot face it then you are useless, just like any other people.

00:10:21.467 --> 00:10:25.234
What's the use of you people getting your realization?

00:10:26.934 --> 00:10:32.334
So now we have to understand that it's not only that we have vibrations,

00:10:32.334 --> 00:10:34.800
that we are all right,

00:10:34.900 --> 00:10:39.067
that you can cure some people is the last word – no.

00:10:39.967 --> 00:10:42.800
You have to spread it, you have to go in the public,

00:10:42.900 --> 00:10:45.900
you have to be collective on this point

00:10:45.934 --> 00:10:47.619
and you have to spread Sahaja Yoga.

00:10:47.700 --> 00:10:53.900
With so many Sahaja yogis all over the world we have not progressed much.

00:10:54.800 --> 00:10:59.234
So now it is you have to plan what you want to do,

00:10:59.334 --> 00:11:02.967
how you want to do it, and how you want to spread Sahaja Yoga.

00:11:03.267 --> 00:11:06.267
It's very important.

00:11:07.767 --> 00:11:14.767
Because you people are good at, say, talking about Sahaja Yoga,

00:11:14.767 --> 00:11:19.234
singing about Sahaja Yoga; all these things are useless unless and until

00:11:19.234 --> 00:11:24.934
you have concrete proof of getting many more people in Sahaja Yoga.

00:11:26.134 --> 00:11:28.200
In a small country like Turkey

00:11:28.800 --> 00:11:32.334
we have 25000 Sahaja yogis, what do you say?

00:11:32.833 --> 00:11:40.733
They are all Muslims, twenty-five thousands Muslim becoming Sahaja yogis,

00:11:41.100 --> 00:11:46.767
while you find that number is very small in any other country.

00:11:47.900 --> 00:11:53.067
They are not very rich, but they care for their Self-realization

00:11:53.267 --> 00:11:56.167
and for toward giving Self-realizations to others.

00:11:56.767 --> 00:12:02.067
It's very surprising how it has worked out, how it has spread.

00:12:02.967 --> 00:12:11.334
So instead of thinking of your problems, of your enemies, of your powers,

00:12:11.767 --> 00:12:13.967
think of giving power to others

00:12:14.167 --> 00:12:18.067
and making them Sahaja Yoga – it's very important.

00:12:18.833 --> 00:12:22.967
If you are in Sahasrara then you have all the powers.

00:12:24.067 --> 00:12:26.967
In Sahasrara if you do not spread Sahaja Yoga,

00:12:27.167 --> 00:12:29.234
what's the use of getting realization?

00:12:29.501 --> 00:12:33.100
Just for yourself – it's being very selfish.

00:12:33.367 --> 00:12:42.267
So I would say that instead of spreading your own glory, your own name,

00:12:42.767 --> 00:12:46.367
please try to get more people to Sahaja Yoga.

00:12:46.967 --> 00:12:50.234
Go into a very dynamic force.

00:12:51.000 --> 00:12:53.134
So many people have complained to Me

00:12:53.733 --> 00:12:57.200
that Sahaja yogis are nothing but dead people.

00:12:58.234 --> 00:13:01.034
Is that what you are?

00:13:02.067 --> 00:13:08.034
Only single person like Me has done so much work, so why not you people?

00:13:08.934 --> 00:13:12.067
In your country have you worked it out all over?

00:13:12.767 --> 00:13:14.334
Just think about it.

00:13:14.867 --> 00:13:18.800
And that's why, unless and until you don't do it you are not sampurna,

00:13:18.833 --> 00:13:20.034
you are not complete,

00:13:20.267 --> 00:13:25.234
and the Adi Shakti's powers you have not understood in its full form.

00:13:26.100 --> 00:13:29.733
That's why I'm telling you today it's a very important day

00:13:29.767 --> 00:13:32.000
that you worship Me as Adi Shakti.

00:13:32.200 --> 00:13:35.867
But you should know that Adi Shakti has to be a complete form.

00:13:36.200 --> 00:13:39.334
It cannot be only half left-sided – no.

00:13:40.900 --> 00:13:44.134
If that doesn't work out, then what's the use?

00:13:44.334 --> 00:13:51.000
It's like any other getting any other realization – that's not so important.

00:13:52.000 --> 00:13:53.800
Not only that you should spread,

00:13:53.967 --> 00:13:58.234
but also you should make them, and realize it.

00:14:05.867 --> 00:14:11.100
All My blessings, all My love, all My powers I give you;

00:14:11.934 --> 00:14:16.234
but try to understand. All right?

00:14:16.900 --> 00:14:18.720
Thank you very much.